Ralph Sollitt, defendant in error, v. Wisconsin Lime & Cement Company, plaintiff in error.Gen. No. 30,824.

O’Connor, J., dissents.

Opinion filed October 13, 1926.N. I. Barry and Cassels, Potter & Bentley, for plaintiff in error. William L. Hart, for defendant in error; William L. Hart and Joseph P. Brodie, of counsel. Mr. Justice Thomson

delivered the opinion of the court.
